  <brief_title>Video-based Counseling &amp; Rapid HIV Testing for Teens</brief_title>
  <official_title>An RCT to Evaluate the Effectiveness of an Emergency Department Based Multimedia HIV Testing Model in Adolescents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
